## Welcome
My name is Bennett Joyce

My biggest accomplishment is **finishing 3rd in my state in skeet shooting.**

My goals for the future are:

1. Go to Furman University for Undergrad and major in Math and minor in Computer Science. 
1. Go to Georgia Tech or Northwestern University for masters in Predictive Analytics.
1. Get an internship/job at leading tech firm (ie. Microsoft, Apple, Google, etc.)
1. Start own company after a few years of learning algorithms and work as a consultant for larger corporations working on Predictive Analytics.
